---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Targy's Twigs - Home">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Every Stick Has a Story</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Collected by Targy the dog on walks and hikes, each twig carries a memory and a bit of adventure</p>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p>
        Welcome to Targy's Twigs, the ultimate online destination for all things stick-related! This site celebrates the finest collection of sticks ever assembled, curated by none other than Targy, the stick enthusiast, fetch champion, and connoisseur of fine twigs.
      </p>
      <a href="/twigs/blog" class="cta-button">Explore the Collection</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="featured">
    <h2>Why Sticks Matter</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>🌲 Collected</h3>
        <p>Found from the forests and plains across the country, each stick tells a story of Targy's adventures.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>🐕 Cherished</h3>
        <p>These aren't just sticks—they're treasures, each one carefully selected and proudly displayed in Targy's collection.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>✨ Celebrated</h3>
        <p>Join us as we honor the joy, memories, and wagging tails that sticks bring to a dog's life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 2rem;
    background-image: url('/twigs/Hero.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    height: 500px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
    margin-right: calc(50% - 50vw);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: rgba(27, 58, 46, 0.6);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-bg);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    font-size: 4rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-bg);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-bg);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    display: none;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-secondary);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    border-radius: 0;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-highlight);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .featured {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .featured h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-bg);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--color-bg);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      height: 350px;
      padding: 0 1rem;
      background-attachment: scroll;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .cta-button {
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
